☕ Café Sutra – Vintage Coffee Shop Landing Page
Café Sutra is a visually rich, vintage-themed landing page designed for a cozy coffee shop experience. Built using HTML, CSS, and a touch of creative styling, this project includes:

🎨 A full-screen hero section with a sepia-toned vintage background.

📋 An interactive contact form with custom styling.

🍽️ A responsive Explore Menu button with enhanced visibility and hover effects.

🌄 Backgrounds styled using high-quality coffee imagery for immersive ambiance.

💡 Elegant typography using Playfair Display for a luxury-retro feel.

⚙️ Preloader animation for a smooth entry experience.
